    *CAVERUNNER:

	Na drugom nivou upishi "SUB B BOYS" i koristi sledece tastere:

                        'F1'             dodatni zhivoti
                        'F2'               dodatno vreme 
                        'F3'           preskakanje nivoa
  
     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 196 ""
@toc AmigaFront5.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    CHAMPIONS OF KRYNN:
                    
	Pogledaj na ulazu u POOL OF RADIANCE sve detalje za varanja u ovoj
	igri.

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 197 ""
@toc AmigaFront5.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    CHAMPIONSHIP MANAGER 93/94:

	Odaberi  New Game,  Tranmere,  Arrogant, nazovi se "Mr Bulgaria" i
	imacesh oko 34 000 000 za troshak.

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 198 ""
@toc AmigaFront5.guide/main

